java.util.EventListener, Algorithm, AlgorithmListener, GameSolver<MemorylessStrategy>
public class DeadEndSolver
extends AbstractGameSolver<MemorylessStrategy>

This class provides a partial solver for any game. The solver only returns for a player the attractor to dead ends of its opponent.

Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
